---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="section bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row gy-5 lg:gy-0 items-center">
      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-7" data-aos="fade-right">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-4">
          Mon parcours
        </span>

        <h2 class="h2 mb-6 font-bold">
          Co-gérant BTP et créateur de sites : <br/>
          <span class="text-primary">Mon double parcours</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
          <p class="lead font-medium text-gray-700">
            Co-gérant d'une entreprise BTP depuis 10 ans, je vis le quotidien du terrain TOUS LES JOURS :
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>La difficulté à trouver de nouveaux clients malgré la qualité du travail</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Les concurrents qui raflent les chantiers grâce à leur présence en ligne</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Les agences web déconnectées qui proposent des sites à 5000€ sans comprendre nos métiers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Le manque de temps pour s'occuper du digital entre les chantiers</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="p-4 bg-primary/5 border-l-4 border-primary rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">
              J'ai créé mon propre site pour mon entreprise.
              <span class="text-primary">Résultat ? +40% de devis en 3 mois.</span>
            </p>
          </div>

          <p>
            Mes confrères artisans m'ont demandé comment faire. C'est là qu'AWEMA est né : mon activité parallèle pour aider les artisans.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">Le gros avantage :</span> Je suis TOUJOURS sur le terrain.
            Je comprends vos problèmes parce que je les vis au quotidien. AWEMA n'est pas une agence web lambda,
            c'est un artisan qui aide ses confrères.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800">
            Aujourd'hui, j'aide <span class="text-primary font-bold">+300 artisans</span> tout en gérant mon entreprise BTP.
            Cette double casquette me permet de rester connecté à la réalité du terrain.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-blue-50 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">Ma double expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
              Toujours actif dans le BTP + Expert en digital = La combinaison parfaite pour comprendre et résoudre vos problèmes.
              Je ne suis pas un commercial qui vous vend du rêve, je suis un confrère qui partage son expérience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="badge-story">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Co-gérant BTP actif</span>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-story">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 6V5a3 3 0 013-3h2a3 3 0 013 3v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v3.57A22.952 22.952 0 0110 13a22.95 22.95 0 01-8-1.43V8a2 2 0 012-2h2zm2-1a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v1H8V5zm1 5a1 1 0 011-1h.01a1 1 0 110 2H10a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              <path d="M2 13.692V16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2.308A24.974 24.974 0 0110 15c-2.796 0-5.487-.46-8-1.308z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>10 ans sur le terrain</span>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-story">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zM8 7a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 001 1h4a1 1 0 001-1V8a1 1 0 00-1-1H8z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Double expertise BTP + Digital</span>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-story">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>+300 artisans accompagnés</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <a href="/mon-histoire" class="btn btn-primary">
            Découvrir mon parcours complet
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
            Parlons de votre projet
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-5" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main Photo -->
          <div class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img
              src="/images/fondateur-placeholder.jpg"
              alt="Fondateur AWEMA - Co-gérant BTP actif"
              class="w-full h-auto"
              width="500"
              height="600"
              loading="lazy"
              onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27 width=%27500%27 height=%27600%27 viewBox=%270 0 500 600%27%3E%3Crect width=%27500%27 height=%27600%27 fill=%27%23e2e8f0%27/%3E%3Ctext x=%27250%27 y=%27300%27 font-family=%27Arial%27 font-size=%2724%27 fill=%27%2394a3b8%27 text-anchor=%27middle%27%3EPhoto Fondateur%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative Elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>

          <!-- Floating Stats Cards -->
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-3 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0s">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">+40%</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">de devis</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-3 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">4.9/5</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">satisfaction</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .badge-story {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #374151;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .badge-story:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }

  .animate-float {
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .prose ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>